The paper discusses the ethics of self-driving cars, which involves the intersection of several computer science subfields such as cybernetics (cs.CY), robotics (cs.RO), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and emerging technologies (cs.ET). Additionally, the paper touches on political philosophy (cs.PH) as a way to supplement the existing approaches to answering ethical questions in this field.
